com.team6.project.services

Class DataImportService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team6.project.services.DataImportService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataImportServiceLocal

    @Default
public class DataImportService
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataImportServiceLocal
    The data import service. This class is responsible for watching a folder on the server for new files. It will also take delivery of a file from a client directly (e.g. a rest based service). This class will, at startup, begin watching a specified directory for new files.
    Author:
    Eoin Kernan
